4Geeks Academy offers a Cybersecurity Bootcamp designed for aspiring cybersecurity specialists, requiring no prior knowledge. The program spans 16 weeks with three live online classes each week, accommodating up to 16 students per class. Participants will gain foundational skills in Windows, Linux, and network administration while mastering cloud security, penetration testing, and cyber threat intelligence. The completion of the course awards an official certificate recognized by various institutions. The syllabus is available in English and Spanish, with classes conducted in the language of the campus. For further details, visit [4Geeks Academy](https://4geeksacademy.com/us/coding-bootcamps/cybersecurity). stop